<topic id="crypto-key-mgt-cryptoperiod">
    <title>Cryptoperiod</title>
    <body>
        <section>
            <title>Description</title>
            <p>The cryptoperiod specifies the maximum period during which the key is active.
                Cryptographic keys used to protect stored account data must have a defined
                cryptoperiod. In addition, a process for changes at the end of the defined
                cryptoperiod is required.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Implementation</title>
            <table frame="all">
                <tgroup cols="3">
                    <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
